OL,3,CHow good is my local NHS maternity
OL,4,Cunit?
OL,6,FOut of the 27 maternity units in the
OL,7,FMidlands, more than two thirds are
OL,8,Frated as 'Requires Improvement', or
OL,9,Fworse.
OL,11,FNot a single unit has achieved the top
OL,12,Frating of 'Outstanding'.
OL,14,FThe Care Quality Commission, or CQC,
OL,15,Finspects units and draws up a report,
OL,16,Fgiving each unit an overall rating
OL,17,Franging from 'Inadequate' to
OL,18,F'Outstanding'.
