OL,3,CHow good is my local NHS maternity
OL,4,Cunit?
OL,6,FThe CQC's deputy chief executive told
OL,7,Fus, "At some NHS hospital trusts we
OL,8,Fhave found that issues such as the
OL,9,Fquality of staff training; poor risk
OL,10,Fassessment; and a failure to engage
OL,11,Fwith, learn from and listen to the
OL,12,Fneeds of women are still impacting on
OL,13,Fthe safety of services, and we have
OL,14,Fbeen clear with those hospitals where
OL,15,Faction must be taken.
