OL,3,CHow good is my local NHS maternity
OL,4,Cunit?
OL,6,F"The increased national focus on
OL,7,Fmaternity safety is both welcome and
OL,8,Fcrucial to improvement, but as we
OL,9,Fhighlighted in our 2022/23 State of
OL,10,FCare report ` we are yet to see the
OL,11,Fprogress needed and current ratings
OL,12,Fshow too many maternity units where
OL,13,Fthere is more to do.
OL,15,F"Safe, high-quality maternity care for
OL,16,Fall is not an ambitious or unrealistic
OL,17,Fgoal. It should be the minimum
OL,18,Fexpectation for women and babies ` and
OL,19,Fis what staff working in maternity
OL,20,Fservices across the country want to
OL,21,Fprovide.
