OL,3,CHow good is my local NHS maternity
OL,4,Cunit?
OL,6,F"It's not acceptable that maternity
OL,7,Fsafety is still so far from where it
OL,8,Fneeds to be. As a healthcare system,
OL,9,Fwe need to do better for women and for
OL,10,Fbabies."
OL,12,FThe government says that ensuring all
OL,13,Fwomen receive safe and compassionate
OL,14,Fmaternity care is a "priority" and the
OL,15,FNHS says it's putting #186 million a
OL,16,Fyear into growing the maternity
OL,17,Fworkforce, and strengthening
OL,18,Fleadership - and is working with
OL,19,FTrusts to make improvements.
